ective yet simple to implement, making\nit a great candidate for generating complementary item recommendations at any\ne-commerce website.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 28 Nov 2022 00:58:21 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 29 Nov 2022 04:10:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-30"}
