enes) with arbitrary structures grafted to the\nparticle periphery to explain the plethora of optical phenomena observed for\nCQDs across the full range of experimental works.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 28 Nov 2022 09:46:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-15"}
